><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mid1665702990151.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mid1665702990151.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mid1665702990151.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mid1665702990151\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">[GENERAL]</code> section contains configuration settings for compression and encoding of binary data, such as images.\n </p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18602e1_d18603e1_d18604e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Configuration file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">psdfef.txt</span> (Unix\n                     only)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mid1665702990151_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mid1665702990151__codeblock_eh5_4lm_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">\n[GENERAL]\ncompression: flate | rle | none\nencoding: asc85 | hex</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mid1665702990151__section_exr_2k1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d157365e80\">Arguments</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__1\">Setting</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__2\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__3\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"3\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">compression</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">rle</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__3\">Run Length Encoding (RLE) compression\n                                algorithm. The resulting compressed binary data is not larger than\n                                the original binary data.<p class=\"p\">This is suitable for 2-color images\n                                    (black and white, no gray-scale), such as line art.</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">flate</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__3\">Compression algorithm based on the\n                                open-source data compression library <span class=\"ph filepath\">zlib</span>. It\n                                requires a PostScript Level 3 printer.<p class=\"p\">This is suitable for most\n                                    full-color or gray-scale images.</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">none</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__3\">No compression (default)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">encoding</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">asc85</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__3\">ASCII85 encoding. 4 bytes of binary data\n                                is encoded to 5 ASCII characters. resulting in a 25% increase in the\n                                output PostScript file. It requires PostScript level 2 or\n                                    above.<p class=\"p\">This encoding is widely supported by printer\n                                    manufacturers.</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">hex</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mid1665702990151__table_d18605e1_d18606e1_d18607e1__entry__3\">2-byte encoding. 1 byte of binary data\n                                is encoded to 2 ASCII characters, resulting in the a 100% increase\n                                in the output PostScript file.<p class=\"p\">Because hex encoding was supported\n                                    in the original PostScript specification, it is a fallback\n                                    option if <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">encoding</span> is not\n                                specified.</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mid1665702990151__pre_cmy_ylm_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[GENERAL]\n#compression: rle\n#compression: flate\ncompression: none\n#encoding: hex\nencoding: asc85</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529929\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529929\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[GENERAL] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The [GENERAL] section contains configuration settings for compression and encoding of binary data, such as images. Configuration file: psdfef.txt (Unix only) Explain this code [GENERAL] compression: flate | rle | none encoding: asc85 | hex Copy Arguments Setting Value Meaning compression rle Run Length Encoding (RLE) compression algorithm. The resulting compressed binary data is not larger than the original binary data. This is suitable for 2-color images (black and white, no gray-scale), such as line art. flate Compression algorithm based on the open-source data compression library zlib . It requires a PostScript Level 3 printer. This is suitable for most full-color or gray-scale images. none No compression (default) encoding asc85 ASCII85 encoding. 4 bytes of binary data is encoded to 5 ASCII characters. resulting in a 25% increase in the output PostScript file. It requires PostScript level 2 or above. This encoding is widely supported by printer manufacturers. hex 2-byte encoding. 1 byte of binary data is encoded to 2 ASCII characters, resulting in the a 100% increase in the output PostScript file. Because hex encoding was supported in the original PostScript specification, it is a fallback option if encoding is not specified. For example: [GENERAL] #compression: rle #compression: flate compression: none #encoding: hex encoding: asc85 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}